{"tid":1530821,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[外國文宣] 公開招募建構反送中運動YouTube channel","createTime":"2019-09-02T05:12:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T05:32:18.000Z","uid":164634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"58f6051dbcbf03dbe650c20dfb554ec3f1a1f05e","tid":1530821,"uid":164634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:12:32.000Z","msg":"反送中運動已經發展左三個月<br />\n大家都有目共睹外國媒體關注係幾重要<br />\n對中國係國際舞台上既角色<br />\n西方媒體報導係有一定影響力<br />\n而外國朋友如身處外地只能靠主流而有公信力既媒體了解事件<br />\n往往忽略事件細節同運動人士既第一身感受<br />\n<br />\nYouTube channel 其實係社會事件上既影響力都好大<br />\n有多人接觸資訊都係靠YouTube or social media <br />\n而YouTube video 有聲有畫可令成件事更生動<br />\n當然事件既fact-check 係非常重要<br />\n但有一個channel host 都帶動整個YouTube channel <br />\n講述事件都好重要<br />\n咁可以引起更多人留意<br />\n<br />\n例如infowars 雖然有多on9野同fakenews <br />\n但follow人數有目共睹<br />\n我地走既路線當然唔係infowars <br />\n但同樣係一個有主持人lead 内容圍繞反送中運動既YouTube channel <br />\n所以我希望可以建構一個channel 令更多外國人活生生地接觸我地既抗爭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但有一個"},{"pid":"823ee7105a7bbf02a474c29cb09b0bc5145fc662","tid":1530821,"uid":164634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:12:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dc20eeea1bd86a49dabade037023dfb02cbb45db","tid":1530821,"uid":164634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:12:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"06518bec7582fffd6cbd40124e2fd1dadbc45b37","tid":1530821,"uid":164634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:13:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5a0306b32088ee5d4fb4e6c86711f9202be5b839","tid":1530821,"uid":164634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:13:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6d3a0ab4b77e85e45ffa42dbb9a5970ff9b94e66","tid":1530821,"uid":164634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:13:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4ad0661e1fb661b61f062a1ceae7ef09d1696808","tid":1530821,"uid":164634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"